data.description:
Welcome HOME to 1524 W 12th St! This immaculate 3-bedroom, 1.5-bathroom home is ideally situated within walking distance to
Lakeview Beach and Lakeview Park, offering a perfect blend of comfort and convenience. Nestled in a sought-after neighborhood, this home provides easy access to the serene Lakeview Beach and the picturesque Lakeview Park, creating an idyllic setting for daily strolls and relaxation. Seamless access to highways, shopping centers, dining establishments, and local amenities, this location caters to a dynamic lifestyle, ensuring that everything you need is within reach. Step inside to discover a meticulously maintained interior, featuring freshly painted walls throughout all rooms. The first floor boasts beautiful hardwood floors, adding a touch of elegance to the living spaces. Upstairs, enjoy the comfort of newer carpeting. The home has been thoughtfully updated, including renovated bathrooms that exude a contemporary charm. A gas-burning fireplace enhances the cozy ambiance, perfect for chilly evenings and creating a warm focal point in the living area. The basement is home to a versatile rec room, providing an ideal space for entertainment, hobbies, or even a home office. Additionally, an enclosed front porch offers a tranquil spot to unwind and enjoy the changing seasons. The private backyard is embraced by a wooden fence, creating a secluded retreat for outdoor activities, gatherings, or simply enjoying a quiet moment in nature. Your next HOME not only offers a comfortable and updated living space but also provides a location that blends the tranquility of Lakeview with the convenience of nearby amenities. Don't miss the opportunity to make this charming property your next HOME!
